%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20launched%20a%20startup%20after%20pivoting%20my%20career%20in%20my%2040s.%20Here's%20what%20I've%20learned%20about%20securing%20investment%20from%20big%20names%20like%20Uber.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22872%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiya%20Gordon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675342594adc4cc134351b5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22654%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETiya%20Gordon%20pivoted%20from%20her%20career%20in%20design%20to%20launch%20an%20electric%20vehicle%20charging%20startup.%3Cp%3EDeborah%20Feingold%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETiya%20Gordon%20worked%20in%20design%20before%20she%20pivoted%20to%20cofounded%20It's%20Electric%2C%20a%20climate%20tech%20startup.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGordon%20launched%20the%20company%20in%202022%20after%20struggling%20to%20find%20an%20accessible%20EV%20charger%20in%20Brooklyn.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20shared%20how%20they%20raised%20%2411%20million%20in%20grants%20and%20investment%20from%20prominent%20investors%20like%20Uber.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Tiya%20Gordon%2C%2045%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20electric%20charging%20startup%20It's%20Electric.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20a%20New%20Yorker%20and%20a%20staunch%20believer%20in%20public%20transportation.%20For%20most%20of%20my%20life%2C%20I%20never%20owned%20a%20car.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20all%20the%20forms%20of%20public%20transportation%20I%20used%20daily%20were%20unsafe.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20to%20think%20about%20how%20I%20could%20transport%20my%20then-five-year-old%20and%20how%20I%20would%20reach%20family%20members%20if%20something%20terrible%20happened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20considered%20getting%20a%20car%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20I%20made%20this%20list%3A%20It%20was%20written%20in%20Sharpie%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20grid%20paper%2C%20and%20it%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNew%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BUsed%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BEV%3F%3F%3F%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20I%20had%20to%20immediately%20eliminate%20electric%20vehicles%20from%20my%20potential%20options%20because%2C%20in%202020%2C%20there%20was%20no%20accessible%20place%20to%20charge%20them%20in%20Brooklyn.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20realized%20there%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20infrastructure%20to%20transition%20to%20EV%20cars%20and%20that%20was%20the%20seed%20idea%20for%20my%20company.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20my%20career%20was%20in%20design%2C%20I%20pivoted%20and%20cofounded%20a%20climate%20tech%20startup%20called%20It's%20Electric%20in%202022.%20We're%20focused%20on%20scaling%20electric%20vehicle%20charging%20in%20densely%20populated%20cities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe're%20now%20a%20company%20of%2010%20people%20and%20we've%20received%20%2411.8%20million%20in%20funding%20and%20grants.%20Uber%20invested%20in%20our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Falleywatch.com%2F2024%2F07%2Fitselectric-curbside-charging-public-platform-nyc-level-2-metered-tiya-gordon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eseed%20round%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20My%20best%20advice%20is%20to%20find%20simple%20solutions%20to%20big%20pain%20points%20and%20prove%20your%20work%20with%20receipts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c88ce2ea-7bf5-4894-a167-81b16f6926db%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20found%20a%20simple%20solution%20for%20electric%20charging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20started%20building%20It's%20Electric%20in%202021%2C%20my%20cofounder%20and%20I%20conducted%20research%20to%20determine%20what%20was%20preventing%20EV%20chargers%20from%20being%20deployed%20quickly%20and%20at%20scale%20in%20US%20cities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20city%20like%20London%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20lampposts%20that%20have%20been%20retrofitted%20into%20curbside%20chargers%20because%20they%20can%20handle%20220%20to%20240%20volts%20of%20electricity.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20the%20power%20feeds%20in%20our%20lamposts%20are%20typically%20much%20lower%2C%20at%20110%20volts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20we%20wanted%20to%20have%20lamppost%20chargers%2C%20we'd%20need%20to%20upgrade%20the%20utility%20main%20and%20corresponding%20interconnection%20agreement%2C%20load%20analysis%2C%20transformer%2C%20submeter%2C%20and%20customer%20connection%20box.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20discovered%20that%20one%20asset%20in%20cities%2C%20that%20has%20plenty%20of%20power%20ready%20to%20go%2C%20is%20buildings%2C%20which%20we%20can%20use%20to%20power%20public%20chargers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20a%20library%2C%20home%2C%20or%20commercial%20building%20agrees%20to%20power%20a%20public%20charger%2C%20we%20share%20revenue%20with%20that%20building%20to%20give%20them%20passive%20income%20as%20an%20incentive.%20It's%20a%20very%20simple%20idea.%20We%20say%20it's%20not%20deep%20tech%2C%20it's%20shallow%20tech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226584f5f2-4d4c-4f8c-aefe-7444ae333373%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ERunning%20a%20pilot%20helped%20get%20investors%20on%20board%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20business%20started%20with%20just%20us%20two%20founders%2C%20but%20after%20we%20raised%20a%20%242.2%20million%20pre-seed%20round%20in%20May%202023%2C%20we%20hired%20our%20first%20two%20employees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20our%20pre-seed%20stage%2C%20multiple%20investors%20told%20me%20that%20our%20idea%20was%20so%20simple%20that%20it%20must%20not%20work%2C%20or%20surely%20someone%20else%20was%20already%20doing%20it.%20We%20had%20to%20prove%20that%20a%20simple%20solution%20could%20be%20effective.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20way%20we%20did%20that%20was%20by%20getting%20our%20pilot%20off%20the%20ground%20in%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20secured%20our%20partnership%20with%20Hyundai%20after%20winning%20their%20EV%20Open%20Innovation%20Challenge.%20Winners%20were%20selected%20based%20on%20their%20potential%20to%20expand%20market%20access%20to%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20knew%20we%20needed%20to%20test%20in%20the%20real%20world%20and%20in%20a%20notoriously%20hard-to-open%20city.%20So%20we%20approached%20the%20New%20York%20City%20Economic%20Development%20Corporation%20to%20ask%20if%20we%20could%20pilot%20our%20technology%20on%20their%20buildings%20in%20the%20Brooklyn%20Army%20Terminal.%20After%20much%20work%2C%20this%20became%20our%20first%20pilot%20and%20was%20crucial%20to%20landing%20investment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20work%20on%20this%20pilot%20was%20so%20successful%20that%20EDC%20launched%20a%20brand%20new%20program%20based%20on%20our%20pilot.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2200bd3c71-c2fc-4262-9f23-8b4ace305ed8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20receipts%20and%20discuss%20your%20wins%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20pilot%20demonstrated%20that%20our%20solution%20offsets%20emissions%2C%20and%20we%20could%20collect%20data%20from%20the%20demo%20to%20show%20it%20was%20scalable%2C%20low-cost%2C%20and%20quick%20to%20install.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pilot%20meant%20I%20could%20provide%20investors%20with%20proven%20results.%20We'd%20gone%20beyond%20what%20investors%20expected%20of%20us%2C%20which%20placated%20their%20queries%20and%20also%20attracted%20investors%20we%20hadn't%20yet%20spoken%20to.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaving%20a%20small-scale%20demonstration%20of%20your%20solution%20is%20more%20helpful%20in%20pitching%20to%20a%20large%20corporation%20than%20trying%20to%20sell%20a%20concept.%20It%20meant%20we%20were%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20a%20Series%20A%20level%20of%20progress%20at%20a%20pre-seed%20level.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20many%20investors%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20is%20so%20simple%20and%20such%20a%20good%20idea%2C%20then%20why%20aren't%20others%20already%20doing%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20My%20answer%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BBecause%20no%20one%20else%20is%20doing%20it%2C%20we%20are%20the%20first.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3EMy%20advice%20to%20founders%20is%20to%20be%20tenacious%20but%20make%20sure%20you%20have%20the%20receipts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20talked%20about%20our%20wins%2C%20such%20as%20prize%20nominations%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fastcompany.com%2F90979335%2Fnext-big-things-tech-sustainability-energy-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emedia%20acknowledgments%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20to%20show%20investors%20that%2C%20by%20the%20jury%20of%20peers%2C%20our%20solution%20is%20winning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1bff2f7-bedc-4be7-af24-b42c471bf32d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EUber%20invested%20in%20our%20seed%20round%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%202024%2C%20we%20closed%20our%20%246.5%20million%20seed%20round%2C%20which%20was%20co-led%20by%20a%20Nordic%20fund%2C%20Failup%20Ventures%2C%20and%20Uber.%20Now%2C%20we're%20a%20team%20of%2010.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20involvement%20with%20Uber%20began%20when%20we%20met%20representatives%20from%20the%20company%20at%20a%20conference.%20Everyone%20thinks%20of%20companies%20like%20Uber%20as%20big%20corporate%20giants%2C%20but%20we%20started%20our%20partnership%20with%20them%20by%20chance.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20sales%20or%20business%20meeting%3B%20it%20was%20just%20two%20optimistic%20people%20working%20in%20transportation%20who%20had%20a%20great%20conversation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20big%20challenge%20to%20Uber's%20zero-emissions%20goal%20is%20that%20Uber%20drivers%20live%20in%20cities%20and%20don't%20have%20garages%2C%20so%20it's%20really%20hard%20to%20charge%20electric%20vehicles.%20We%20provided%20a%20cheap%2C%20fast%20solution%20for%20urban%20drivers%20to%20charge%20electric%20cars.%20Uber%20needed%20more%20drivers%20to%20adopt%20electric%20cars%20to%20reach%20its%20goals%2C%20and%20we%20pitched%20ourselves%20as%20that%20stepping%20stone.%20A%20series%20of%20productive%20conversations%20helped%20us%20build%20this%20partnership.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaving%20Uber%20support%20our%20solution%20has%20been%20a%20great%20validation%20for%20our%20startup.%20It's%20also%20meant%20we've%20had%20access%20to%20smart%20people%20on%20their%20team%20to%20understand%20different%20policies%20and%20how%20we%20can%20help%20meet%20city%20goals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20advice%20for%20founders%20who%20want%20to%20develop%20relationships%20with%20established%20companies%20is%20to%20try%20to%20solve%20problems%20for%20other%20people.%20Don't%20say%20you%20want%20a%20partnership%20because%20of%20what%20it%20can%20do%20for%20your%20startup%2C%20but%20put%20yourself%20out%20there%20as%20the%20problem-solver%20for%20a%20larger%20corporation.%20You%20want%20to%20find%20their%20pain%20point%20and%20point%20out%20that%20there%20isn't%20a%20solution%20that's%20already%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-pivot-40s-launched-startup-investment-lessons-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733651402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6753450e8fb3f94e5073f447%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-pivot-40s-launched-startup-investment-lessons-2024-12%22%2C%22summ