week%20as%20of%20October%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Alphabet-owned%20company%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20expand%20its%20service%20to%20the%20public%20in%20Miami%20by%202026.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneral-motors-robotaxi-patent-pedestrian-bullying-vandalism-cruise-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733649061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67550dc48fbb2783ed307161%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneral-motors-robotaxi-patent-pedestrian-bullying-vandalism-cruise-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22General%20Motors%2C%20which%20operates%20Cruise%20robotaxis%2C%20filed%20a%20patent%20that%20shows%20how%20robotaxis%20could%20respond%20to%20%26quot%3Badversarial%26quot%3B%20pedestrians%20on%20the%20road.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneral-motors-robotaxi-patent-pedestrian-bullying-vandalism-cruise-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ozempic%20knock-offs%20are%20rife%20with%20scams%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225056%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shattered%20Ozempic%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6745fd769f2901eb6036f6a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222529%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Jenny%20Chang-Rodriguez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKelly%20is%20aware%20that%20she%20should%20have%20been%20more%20careful%20when%20she%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20weight-loss%20medication%20online.%20She%20knows%20she%20should%20have%20looked%20into%20the%20company%20selling%20it%2C%20but%2C%20as%20she%20puts%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Bdesperate%20times%20call%20for%20desperate%20measures.%26quot%3B%20She%20had%20gastric-bypass%20surgery%20in%202011%2C%20and%20that%20worked%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20then%20she%20started%20to%20gain%20the%20weight%20back%20after%20the%20%26quot%3Bfood%20noise%26quot%3B%20returned.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20alcohol%20where%20you%20can%20abstain%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20eat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20she%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20subscription%20with%20Zealthy%2C%20a%20telehealth%20company%20she%20found%20through%20Google.%20It%20seemed%20simple%20enough%3A%20She%20was%20charged%20a%20subscription%20fee%20and%20a%20fee%20for%20the%20medication%20she%20ordered%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsemaglutide-how-does-drug-work-for-weight-loss-diabetes-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esemaglutide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20basically%20generic%20Ozempic.%20She%20quickly%20noticed%20her%20food%20cravings%20and%20appetite%20had%20decreased.%20About%20six%20weeks%20later%2C%20she%20noticed%20she%20was%20losing%20weight.%20But%20then%20the%20billing%20got%20weird.%20Screenshots%20of%20the%20company's%20billing%20portal%20show%20that%20in%20September%20she%20was%20charged%20three%20times%20for%20one%20medication%20on%20top%20of%20the%20subscription%20fee%20and%20a%20separate%20%26quot%3Bmanual%20entry%26quot%3B%20charge%20of%20nearly%20%24400.%20In%20October%2C%20her%20medication%20never%20arrived%3B%20the%20company%20blamed%20shipping%20delays%20on%20hurricanes%20in%20Florida.%20She%20tried%20to%20resolve%20the%20problem%20through%20the%20company's%20chat%20service%20and%20emails%2C%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20medication%20or%20a%20refund%2C%20but%20eventually%2C%20she%20gave%20up%20after%20failing%20to%20make%20progress%20on%20either%20front.%20She%20canceled%20the%20card%20she%20had%20on%20the%20account%20to%20prevent%20further%20charges.%20After%20filing%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Better%20Business%20Bureau%2C%20Kelly%2C%20which%20is%20a%20pseudonym%2C%20has%20gotten%20some%20of%20her%20money%20back%2C%20but%20she's%20still%20out%20hundreds%20of%20dollars.%20Zealthy%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20topic%20of%20embarrassment%20came%20up%20throughout%20our%20conversation.%20Kelly%20has%20been%20overweight%20her%20whole%20life%2C%20and%20many%20people%20aren't%20particularly%20nice%20about%20it%20%E2%80%94%20they%20don't%20understand%20why%20she%20can't%20manage%20with%20just%20diet%20and%20exercise.%20%26quot%3BMy%20pants%20don't%20fit%20if%20I%20so%20much%20as%20look%20at%20a%20cookie%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20The%20experience%20with%20Zealthy%20only%20added%20to%20this%20sense%20of%20ostracism.%20Kelly's%20ashamed%20that%20she%20gained%20the%20weight%20back%2C%20that%20she%20let%20her%20guard%20down%2C%20and%20that%20she%20was%20taken%20for%20a%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Kelly%20isn't%20alone%3A%20The%20explosion%20of%20new%20weight-loss%20medications%20has%20opened%20the%20door%20for%20all%20sorts%20of%20questionable%20business%20practitioners%20and%20outright%20scams.%20Drugs%20promising%20to%20help%20people%20lose%20weight%20are%20everywhere%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20society%20prizes%20being%20thin%20%E2%80%94%20and%20punishes%20those%20who%20aren't%20%E2%80%94%20makes%20vulnerable%20people%20susceptible%20to%20tricks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediabetes%20and%20weight-loss%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%20semaglutide%20and%20tirzepatide%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20generally%20referred%20to%20as%20GLP-1s%20and%20which%20you%20probably%20know%20by%20the%20names%20Ozempic%20or%20Wegovy%2C%20made%20by%20Novo%20Nordisk%2C%20and%20Mounjaro%20or%20Zepbound%2C%20made%20by%20Eli%20Lilly%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20game%20changers%20in%20obesity%20treatment%20and%20management.%20For%20people%20struggling%20with%20their%20weight%2C%20these%20drugs%20can%20seem%20like%20a%20miracle.%20But%20because%20the%20brand-name%20medications%20are%20so%20expensive%20and%20difficult%20to%20get%2C%20many%20people%2C%20like%20Kelly%2C%20are%20turning%20to%20other%20sources%2C%20buying%20copycats%20from%20online%20telehealth%20companies%20and%20sellers%20that%20have%20very%20little%2C%20if%20any%2C%20oversight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompounded%20versions%20of%20the%20drugs%20have%20been%20effective%20for%20many%20people%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffda-warns-against-risks-compounded-semaglutide-ozempic-online-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeven%20if%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20doesn't%20approve%20them%20and%20has%20warned%20against%20taking%20them%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20not%20everyone%20has%20been%20so%20lucky.%20In%20Kelly's%20case%2C%20she's%20out%20a%20chunk%20of%20money.%20(She's%20not%20the%20only%20one%20with%20issues%20with%20Zealthy%3A%20The%20federal%20government%20has%20sued%20the%20company%2C%20alleging%20unfair%20and%20deceptive%20conduct%20including%20billing%20customers%20for%20things%20they%20didn't%20knowingly%20agree%20to%20and%20misleading%20people%20about%20their%20subscriptions.)%20For%20others%2C%20the%20consequences%20are%20not%20only%20financial%20but%20medical.%20Poison-control%20centers%20reported%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F12%2F13%2Fhealth%2Fsemaglutide-overdoses-wellness%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenormous%20jump%20in%20semaglutide-related%20calls%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamanetworkopen%2Ffullarticle%2F2821882%3Futm_source%3DFor_The_Media%26utm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_campaign%3Dftm_links%26utm_term%3D080224%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOne%20recent%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20looking%20at%20websites%20advertising%20semaglutide%20without%20a%20prescription%20found%20that%2042%25%20of%20the%20sites%20belonging%20to%20online%20pharmacies%20were%20part%20of%20illegal%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20a%20little%20bit%20in%20the%20Wild%20West%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20John%20Hertig%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20Butler%20University's%20College%20of%20Pharmacy%20and%20Health%20Sciences.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20exploded%20so%20fast.%20There's%20so%20much%20money%20to%20be%20made%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20marketplace%20is%20awash%20in%20companies%20trying%20to%20ride%20the%20Ozempic%20wave%20by%20selling%20compounded%20semaglutide%2C%20knockoff%20drugs%2C%20and%20similar-sounding%20supplements.%20Last%20year%20NBC%20News%20found%20that%20there%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Ftech%2Finternet%2Fozempic-weight-loss-drug-ads-instagram-wegovy-semaglutide-rcna88602%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20ads%20on%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20mentioning%20semaglutide%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20there%20were%20ads%20for%20Viagra%20on%20the%20platforms.%20Semaglutide%20content%20is%20all%20over%20TikTok%2C%20much%20of%20it%20dubious.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-wegovy-scams-phishing-cyber-security-mcafee-ai-facebook-craigslist-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPhishing%20scams%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20use%20the%20medications%20as%20the%20hook%20have%20increased%2C%20as%20have%20other%20schemes%20designed%20to%20get%20people's%20data%20or%20payment%20information%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20access%20to%20the%20drugs.%20Reddit%20and%20the%20Better%20Business%20Bureau's%20website%20are%20filled%20with%20complaints%20about%20telehealth%20companies%20offering%20GLP-1%20products%20%E2%80%94%20people%20describe%20unwittingly%20signing%20up%20for%20pricey%20subscriptions%2C%20never%20receiving%20medication%2C%20or%20finding%20it%20impossible%20to%20quit.%20It%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20discern%20a%20safe%2C%20legitimate%20offer%20from%20a%20dupe.%20Complicating%20things%20is%20that%20the%20FDA%20hasn't%20clearly%20established%20what's%20OK%20here%2C%20leaving%20consumers%20to%20figure%20things%20out%20for%20themselves.%20Even%20big-name%20telehealth%20companies%20are%20sending%20medications%20to%20patients%20without%20a%20lot%20of%20supervision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20medication%20carries%20a%20risk%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20affect%20everyone%20equally%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jessica%20Bartfield%2C%20a%20clinical%20associate%20professor%20at%20Wake%20Forest%20University's%20Bariatric%20and%20Weight%20Management%20Center.%20%26quot%3BSo%20when%20you%20see%20these%20images%20and%20testimonials%20and%20stories%20about%20people%20who%20are%20on%20it%20for%20maybe%20inappropriate%20purposes%20or%20who%20are%20losing%20tremendous%20weight%20or%20who%20aren't%20being%20monitored%20the%20right%20way%2C%20then%20it%20normalizes%20it%2C%20and%20people%20think%20that%20that's%20OK.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20body-positive%20movement%20has%20spread%20the%20message%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20or%20two%20that%20you%20can%20and%20should%20love%20your%20body%20at%20any%20size%20and%20that%20health%20and%20beauty%20are%20not%20synonymous%20with%20thinness.%20That%20movement%20isn't%20necessarily%20a%20failure%2C%20but%20the%20rush%20to%20get%20semaglutide%20shows%20that%20American%20culture's%20preference%20toward%20skinny%20never%20went%20away%2C%20said%20Natalia%20Mehlman%20Petrzela%2C%20a%20history%20professor%20at%20The%20New%20School%20who%20wrote%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BFit%20Nation%3A%20The%20Gains%20and%20Pains%20of%20America's%20Exercise%20Obsession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20clear%20that%20there%20are%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20%E2%80%94%20medical%20issues%20aside%20%E2%80%94%20really%20want%20to%20be%20thin%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20the%20FDA%20and%20doctors%20might%20tell%20people%20that%20off-brand%20semaglutide%20and%20other%20products%20are%20risky%2C%20people%20aren't%20necessarily%20deterred%20from%20seeking%20them%20out.%20They%20see%20others%20getting%20results%2C%20and%20they%20want%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20see%20this%20with%20cancer%20treatment.%20You%20don't%20see%20this%20with%20blood-pressure%20medications.%20You%20don't%20see%20this%20with%20antibiotics%2C%26quot%3B%20Bartfield%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%20unique%20field%2C%20and%20I%20can%20appreciate%20the%20appeal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rush%20of%20gray-market%20semaglutide%20and%20scams%20riffing%20on%20the%20desire%20for%20the%20drugs%20are%20a%20confluence%20of%20market%20need%20and%20market%20want%20%E2%80%94%20some%20people%20who%20really%20do%20need%20to%20lose%20weight%20for%20medical%20reasons%20are%20turning%20to%20alternative%20methods%20because%20they%20can't%20get%20or%20afford%20the%20%26quot%3Bofficial%26quot%3B%20stuff%2C%20while%20others%20are%20using%20the%20medications%20more%20out%20of%20vanity.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20pursuit%20of%20dubious%20miracle%20products%20in%20the%20name%20of%20being%20thin%20and%20attractive%20has%20existed%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20Jane%20Fonda%20tells%20stories%20of%20mailing%20away%20for%20tapeworms%2C%26quot%3B%20Mehlman%20Petrzela%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20'90s%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20is%20an%20approved%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20Olestra%20was%20a%20fat%20substitute%2C%20and%20the%20warning%20was%20anal%20leakage.%20And%20people%20were%20like%2C%20'OK%2C%20whatever%2C%20if%20it%20makes%20you%20skinny.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20promise%20of%20being%20thin%20is%20an%20incredibly%20effective%20marketing%20tactic%20and%20one%20that's%20hard%20to%20resist%2C%20especially%20with%20this%20new%20class%20of%20drugs.%20My%20Instagram%20feed%20is%20filled%20with%20nearly%20indistinguishable%20ads%20for%20weight-loss%20medications%20that%20show%20a%20little%20vial%20of%20some%20clear%20substance%2C%20list%20facts%20and%20figures%20about%20weight%20loss%2C%20and%20mention%20how%20expensive%20the%20real%20stuff%20is.%20Sometimes%20it%20takes%20me%20a%20second%20to%20realize%20I'm%20looking%20at%20an%20ad%2C%20because%20it's%20just%20a%20person%20talking%20to%20the%20camera.%20Mehlman%20Petrzela%20told%20me%20she%20often%20sees%20ads%20for%20supplements%20promising%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bnature's%20Ozempic%26quot%3B%20on%20her%20feed.%20An%20acquaintance%20recently%20mentioned%20that%20after%20seeing%20all%20the%20ads%2C%20she%20signed%20up%20with%20a%20telehealth%20company%20to%20see%20if%20she%20qualified%20to%20get%20compounded%20semaglutide.%20After%20a%20consultation%2C%20she%20was%20denied.%20(She's%20quite%20thin%20and%20pretty%20clearly%20didn't%20need%20them.)%20But%20then%2C%20months%20later%2C%20she%20noticed%20the%20company%20had%20been%20quietly%20withdrawing%20%2430%20from%20her%20bank%20account%20each%20month.%20She'd%20missed%20it%20because%20the%20purchases%20were%20categorized%20as%20%26quot%3Bgroceries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Feinberg%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F23693881.fs1.hubspotusercontent-na1.net%2Fhubfs%2F23693881%2Freports%2FDCA_OZEMPIC_SCAMS_TIKTOK.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearched%20Ozempic%20scams%20on%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20role%20as%20vice%20president%20of%20content%20moderation%20at%20the%20Coalition%20for%20a%20Safer%20Web.%20He%20told%20me%20the%20social-media%20platform's%20algorithm%20is%20good%20at%20sending%20people%20down%20a%20%26quot%3Brabbit%20hole%26quot%3B%20of%20content%20once%20it%20figures%20out%20they%20might%20be%20interested%20in%20losing%20weight.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20searching%20TikTok%20videos%20on%20Ozempic%3B%20it's%20coming%20right%20through%20my%20feed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20danger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20his%20research%2C%20Feinberg%20engages%20with%20people%20purporting%20to%20be%20selling%20Ozempic%20or%20some%20version%20of%20it%20on%20TikTok.%20He%20sent%20screenshots%20of%20one%20of%20his%20recent%20exchanges%20with%20an%20account%20called%20Ozempicweightloos0%20where%20the%20seller%20sent%20over%20a%20list%20of%20prices%20ranging%20from%20%2490%20for%200.25%20milligrams%20of%20Ozempic%20to%20%24110%20for%201%20mg.%20(For%20comparison%2C%20Novo%20Nordisk's%20website%20lists%20the%20price%20of%201%20mg%20of%20Ozempic%20as%20%24968.52.)%20The%20account%20stopped%20responding%20after%20he%20asked%20where%20the%20medication%20shipped%20from.%20It's%20a%20type%20of%20conversation%20he's%20had%20often%20%E2%80%94%20and%20alerted%20lawmakers%20and%20TikTok%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Jabbara%2C%20a%20senior%20vice%20president%20and%20global%20head%20of%20fraud%20services%20at%20Visa%2C%20said%20it%20saw%20a%20huge%20spike%20in%20chatter%20on%20the%20dark%20web%20about%20weight-loss%20scams%20in%20May%20and%20June.%20He%20posited%20that%20it%20was%20tied%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization's%20warning%20around%20that%20time%20about%20fake%20semaglutide%3A%20The%20WHO%20noticed%20enough%20nefarious%20activity%20to%20issue%20an%20alert%2C%20triggering%20more%20conversations%20among%20bad%20actors%20about%20how%20well%20the%20scams%20are%20working.%20He%20said%20they%20realize%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20a%20successful%20fraud%20scheme%20that%20is%20yielding%20a%20good%20return%20on%20investment%20for%20us%2C%20so%20we're%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20pursue%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMay%20and%20June%20are%20also%20the%20start%20of%20beach%20season%2C%20when%20people%20are%20looking%20to%20get%20their%20summer%20bodies%20%E2%80%94%20and%20maybe%20realizing%20it's%20too%20late%20unless%20they%20take%20some%20extreme%20measures.%20%26quot%3BFraudsters%20are%20very%20attuned%20to%20cultural%20moments%20and%20what%20is%20attractive%20to%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20Jabbara%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20very%20keen%20marketers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20can't%20paint%20all%20the%20operators%20in%20the%20compounded-semaglutide%20and%20GLP-1%20markets%20with%20a%20broad%20brush%2C%20because%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20variation.%20There's%20a%20difference%20between%20major%20telehealth%20companies%20like%20Ro%20or%20Hims%20doling%20out%20prescribed%20medication%20and%20illegal%20pharmacies%20and%20scammers%20on%20WhatsApp%20or%20Telegram%20sending%20medications%20willy-nilly%2C%20if%20at%20all.%20But%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20everyone%20is%20operating%20in%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20gray%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExcept%20for%20the%20really%20sketchy%20stuff%2C%20compounded%20semaglutide%20and%20tirzepatide%20are%20generally%20coming%20from%20compounding%20pharmacies%20that%20make%20customized%20medications.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%20these%20pharmacies%20make%20medications%20for%20people%20with%20unique%20needs%3A%20You%20have%20an%20allergy%20to%20a%20certain%20dye%20usually%20used%20in%20the%20name-brand%20drug%2C%20so%20they%20make%20the%20drug%20without%20it%20for%20you.%20But%20when%20there's%20a%20shortage%20of%20the%20drugs%20%E2%80%94%20as%20there%20has%20been%20for%20GLP-1%20drugs%20%E2%80%94%20the%20rules%20for%20compounding%20get%20a%20little%20looser%2C%20and%20the%20FDA%20allows%20copying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20confusing%20wrinkles.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20shortages%20don't%20last%20forever%2C%20and%20when%20they%20end%2C%20the%20copying%20is%20supposed%20to%20stop.%20The%20FDA%20took%20tirzepatide%20off%20its%20shortage%20list%20in%20the%20fall%2C%20which%20should%20have%20meant%20no%20more%20compounding.%20But%20after%20a%20compounding%20trade%20group%20sued%20the%20FDA%20over%20the%20decision%2C%20it%20said%20it%20would%20reevaluate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENovo%20Nordisk%20and%20Eli%20Lilly%20both%20have%20patents%20on%20their%20drugs%2C%20and%20they're%20not%20eager%20to%20give%20up%20their%20secret%20sauce%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-compounded-semaglutide-online-risks-wegovy-ozempic-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20clear%20how%20close%20the%20compounded%20concoctions%20are%20to%20the%20real%20stuff%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fdrugs%2Fpostmarket-drug-safety-information-patients-and-providers%2Ffdas-concerns-unapproved-glp-1-drugs-used-weight-loss%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20FDA%20has%20warned%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20all%20the%20compounded%20drugs%20are%20risky%2C%20it's%20at%20the%20same%20time%20somewhat%20greenlighting%20them%2C%20people%20are%20being%20inundated%20with%20ads%20for%20them%2C%20and%20people%20are%20trying%20them%20out.%20The%20cat's%20already%20out%20of%20the%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20somewhat%20of%20a%20no-man's-land%20in%20terms%20of%20no%20clear%20regulation%2C%20reduced%20government%20oversight%2C%20and%20a%20straight%20lab-to-lap%20delivery%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anthony%20Mahajan%2C%20a%20founding%20partner%20at%20the%20Health%20Law%20Alliance%2C%20a%20healthcare-focused%20law%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20telehealth%20and%20direct-to-consumer%20GLP-1%20sales%20circumvent%20many%20of%20the%20checkpoints%20in%20traditional%20prescribing.%20Because%20these%20prescriptions%20aren't%20covered%20by%20insurers%20and%20are%20instead%20paid%20for%20directly%20by%20the%20consumer%2C%20there's%20no%20inspection%20by%20the%20government%20or%20insurers%20reviewing%20whether%20a%20drug%20is%20medically%20necessary%20and%20deciding%20whether%20to%20authorize%20payment.%20Compounds%20are%20also%20generally%20exempt%20from%20a%20federal%20law%20meant%20to%20stop%20harmful%20drugs%20from%20getting%20into%20the%20US's%20supply%20chain%2C%20meaning%20checkpoints%20for%20product%20sourcing%20and%20supply-chain%20integrity%20are%20missing.%20%26quot%3BOversight%20agencies%20are%20cut%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20tough%20to%20blame%20consumers%20or%20the%20companies%20distributing%20compounded%20semaglutide%20for%20getting%20into%20this%20business%2C%20given%20how%20expensive%20and%20difficult%20it%20is%20to%20get%20the%20name-brand%20drugs.%20Insurers%20generally%20won't%20cover%20Ozempic%20or%20Mounjaro%20unless%20a%20patient%20has%20diabetes%2C%20meaning%20that%20to%20get%20the%20medications%2C%20people%20who%20want%20to%20use%20them%20for%20weight%20loss%20have%20to%20cough%20up%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20a%20year.%20That's%20assuming%20their%20doctors%20will%20prescribe%20them%2C%20which%2C%20some%20won't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20price%20it%20appropriately%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20enough%20supply%2C%20then%20people%20are%20always%20going%20to%20find%20another%20way%20to%20get%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Hertig%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20sometimes%20that%20other%20way%20to%20get%20it%20is%20safe%2C%20but%20in%20many%20examples%20it's%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20ward%20off%20telehealth%20companies%2C%20Eli%20Lilly%20cut%20the%20price%20of%20Zepbound%20for%20certain%20patients%20who%20order%20directly%20from%20the%20company%2C%20though%20the%20drug%20is%20still%20pricey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20some%20extent%2C%20this%20is%20a%20tale%20as%20old%20as%20time%3A%20People%20want%20to%20be%20thin%20and%20will%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20achieve%20that%2C%20and%20businesses%20are%20happy%20to%20oblige.%20But%20GLP-1%20medications%20do%20seem%20to%20have%20put%20this%20dynamic%20into%20overdrive.%20These%20drugs%20really%20are%20%3Cem%3Eeverywhere%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20in%20commercials%2C%20on%20social%20media%2C%20in%20the%20news%2C%20in%20conversations.%20And%20everyone's%20getting%20into%20the%20semaglutide%20game%3A%20diet%20companies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F03%2F01%2Fbusiness%2Fozempic-wegovy-equinox-life-time-gyms%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egyms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.kroger.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-details%2F2024%2FKroger-Healths-The-Little-Clinic-Announces-Revamped-Weight-Management-Program%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrocery%20stores%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20this%20will%20all%20turn%20out%20fine.%20The%20regular%20versions%20of%20the%20drugs%20will%20become%20more%20available%2C%20and%20the%20generic%20ones%20will%2C%20by%20and%20large%2C%20work%20fine.%20Sure%2C%20there%20will%20be%20scams%3B%20that's%20true%20of%20everything.%20But%20that's%20not%20the%20only%20possible%20outcome.%20Many%20people%20may%20wind%20up%20not%20only%20losing%20money%20but%20also%20harming%20their%20bodies%20by%20injecting%20medications%20that%20aren't%20safe.%20And%20these%20medications%20are%20so%20new%20that%20it's%20hard%20not%20to%20worry%20that%20in%20five%20or%2010%20years%20we'll%20wonder%20why%20we%20allowed%20online%20companies%20to%20send%20compounded%20injected%20drugs%20around%20the%20country%20to%20people%20who%20were%20prescribed%20a%20medication%20after%20completing%20a%20five-minute%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHertig%20said%20he%20expects%20tighter%20and%20clearer%20regulations%20on%20GLP-1s%20in%20the%20years%20ahead%2C%20which%20is%20good%2C%20though%20it%20doesn't%20help%20people%20trying%20to%20sort%20things%20out%20now.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20miracle%20drug%20has%20people%20looking%20for%20miracles%20everywhere%2C%20including%20in%20places%20they%20shouldn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20fall%20for%20traps%20or%20scams%2C%20they're%20often%20hesitant%20to%20admit%20it%20or%20advertise%20it.%20That's%20especially%20true%20for%20weight-loss%20products%20%E2%80%94%20the%20message%20American%20culture%20sends%20is%20that%20you're%20supposed%20to%20be%20thin%20and%20fit%20but%20you're%20not%20supposed%20to%20talk%20about%20how%20you%20do%20it.%20Society%20often%20treats%20being%20overweight%20as%20a%20moral%20failure%20and%20using%20a%20medication%20to%20take%20off%20pounds%20as%20cheating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelly%20hasn't%20given%20up%20on%20semaglutide%20altogether.%20She's%20switched%20providers%20%E2%80%94%20she's%20now%20getting%20her%20medication%20from%20Hers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20continues%20to%20shed%20weight.%20The%20experience%20is%20%26quot%3Bnight%20and%20day.%26quot%3B%20Her%20mom%20is%20nervous%20about%20her%20taking%20medication%20and%20worries%20about%20the%20unknowns%2C%20but%20that%20hasn't%20deterred%20Kelly.%20She%20hasn't%20told%20many%20people%20about%20the%20Zealthy%20experience%2C%20and%20she%20doesn't%20advertise%20that%20she's%20taking%20a%20weight-loss%20drug%2C%20though%20she'll%20be%20honest%20if%20people%20ask.%20Her%20doctor%20has%20been%20reluctant%20to%20prescribe%20her%20a%20GLP-1%20medication%2C%20meaning%20she's%20still%20paying%20out%20of%20pocket.%20She%20thinks%20the%20reluctance%20was%20part%20of%20what%20landed%20her%20in%20a%20bad%20spot%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20makes%20patients%20like%20myself%20especially%20vulnerable%20for%20fraud%20in%20the%20telemedicine%20world.%20We%20want%20and%20need%20to%20lose%20weight%2C%20have%20tried%20everything%2C%20and%20this%20is%20working%20for%20so%20many%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20risks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-zepbound-semaglutide-compound-scams-health-social-media-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733648941000%2C%22vis