2520married%2520parents.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elived%20at%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20their%20parents%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20US%20Census%20data%20published%20this%20year.%20That%20compares%20to%2052%25%20of%20men%20and%2035%25%20of%20women%20in%20that%20age%20range%20who%20were%20living%20with%20their%20parents%20in%201960.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESatayan%20Mahajan%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20financial%20advisory%20firm%20Datalign%20Advisory%2C%20said%20that%20caring%20for%20parents%20and%20children%20simultaneously%20was%20one%20reason%20his%20Gen%20X%20clients%20commonly%20cited%20for%20falling%20behind%20in%20preparing%20for%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarket%20crashes%20during%20formative%20times%20in%20their%20career%2C%20such%20as%20during%20the%20early%202000s%20and%20the%20Great%20Financial%20Crisis%2C%20are%20another%20reason%20why%20many%20have%20less%20saved%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20sandwiched%20portion%20of%20Gen%20Xers%20are%20really%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20trouble.%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20have%20to%20say%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20sound%20so%20negative%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20think%20they're%20in%20a%20tough%20spot%20and%20they%20have%20a%20bunch%20of%20things%20that%20hit%20them%20pretty%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20Mahajan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20outlook%20remains%20uncertain%20for%20Gen%20X.%20While%20boomers%20are%20estimated%20to%20pass%20on%20around%20%2480%20trillion%20in%20wealth%2C%20most%20of%20that%20money%20looks%20primed%20to%20head%20to%20millennials%2C%20not%20Gen%20X%2C%20Mahajan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20kind%20of%20in%20an%20awkward%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20there's%20a%20large%20swath%20of%20Gen%20Xers%20who%20may%20be%20in%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20lurch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUncertainty%20is%20also%20swirling%20around%20the%20availability%20of%20government%20retirement%20funds.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbo.gov%2Fpublicat