arkets%2Fipo%2Fipo-frenzy-5-main-board-6-smes-to-hit-market-to-raise-rs-18-500-cr-124120800226_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Syrians%20storm%20presidential%20palace%2C%20loot%20Assad%E2%80%99s%20personal%20belongings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733643609000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116100718%2Cimgsize-5044124.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fwatch-syrians-storm-presidential-palace-loot-assads-personal-belongings%2Farticleshow%2F116098641.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Syrian%20dictator%20Bashar%20al-Assad%20fled%20Damascus%20as%20opposition%20forces%20entered%20the%20capital%2C%20encountering%20minimal%20resistance.%20Citizens%20celebrated%2C%20storming%20the%20presidential%20palace%20and%20toppling%20Assad%20statues.%20Rebel%20groups%2C%20including%20some%20with%20al-Qaeda%20ties%2C%20seized%20state%20media%20and%20declared%20imminent%20victory%20after%20capturing%20Homs%2C%20a%20key%20city.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fwatch-syrians-storm-presidential-palace-loot-assads-personal-belongings%2Farticleshow%2F116098641.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Where%20Is%20Bashar%20Al-Assad%3F%20Questions%20Over%20Syrian%20President's%20Whereabouts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Syria%20war%20monitor%20said%20that%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad%20has%20left%20the%20country%2C%20after%20losing%20swathes%20of%20territory%20to%20a%20lightning%20offensive%20led%20by%20an%20Islamist-led%20rebel%20coalition%20that%20said%20it%20entered%20Damascus%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20in%20the%20Syrian%20capital%20told%20AFP%20heavy%20gunfire%20rang%20out%2C%20after%20a%20source%20close%20to%20Hezbollah%20saying%20fighters%20from%20the%20key%20Assad%20ally%20had%20left%20their%20positions%20around%20Damascus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president's%20reported%20departure%20comes%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%20after%20the%20Islamist%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20(HTS)%20group%20launched%20its%20campaign%20challenging%20more%20than%20five%20decades%20of%20rule%20by%20the%20Assad%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAssad%20left%20Syria%20via%20Damascus%20international%20airport%20before%20the%20army%20security%20forces%20left%26quot%3B%20the%20facility%2C%26quot%3B%20Rami%20Abdel%20Rahman%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Syrian%20Observatory%20for%20Human%20Rights%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFP%20was%20unable%20to%20immediately%20confirm%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20saying%20their%20forces%20were%20heading%20into%20the%20capital%2C%20HTS%20announced%20an%20%26quot%3Bend%20of%20the%20era%20of%20tyranny%20in%20the%20prison%20of%20Sednaya%26quot%3B%20as%20they%20broke%20into%20the%20jail%20which%20has%20become%20a%20by-word%20for%20darkest%20abuses%20of%20the%20Syrian%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rapid%20developments%20in%20Damascus%20come%20only%20hours%20after%20HTS%20said%20they%20had%20captured%20the%20strategic%20city%20of%20Homs%2C%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%20ministry%20earlier%20denied%20that%20rebels%20had%20entered%20Homs%2C%20describing%20the%20situation%20there%20as%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20and%20stable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoms%20lies%20about%20140%20kilometres%20(85%20miles)%20north%20of%20the%20capital%20and%20was%20the%20third%20major%20city%20seized%20by%20the%20rebels%20who%20began%20their%20advance%20on%20November%2027%2C%20reigniting%20a%20years-long%20war%20that%20had%20become%20largely%20dormant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHezbollah%20fighters%20leave%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonitoring%20events%20in%20Damascus%2C%20the%20Britain-based%20Observatory%20confirmed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20doors%20of%20the%20infamous%20'Sednaya'%20prison...%20have%20been%20opened%20for%20thousands%20of%20detainees%20who%20were%20imprisoned%20by%20the%20security%20apparatus%20throughout%20the%20regime's%20rule%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Assad's%20government%20denied%20the%20army%20had%20withdrawn%20from%20areas%20around%20Damascus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20very%20strong%20security%20and%20military%20cordon%26quot%3B%20was%20being%20established%20by%20the%20armed%20forces%20around%20the%20capital%20%26quot%3Band%20no%20one...%20can%20penetrate%20this%20defensive%20line%26quot%3B%2C%20Interior%20Minister%20Mohammed%20al-Rahmoun%20told%20state%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssad%20has%20for%20years%20been%20backed%20by%20Lebanese%20Hezbollah%2C%20whose%20forces%20%26quot%3Bvacated%20their%20positions%20around%20Damascus%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20%26quot%3Bhas%20instructed%20its%20fighters%20in%20recent%20hours%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20Homs%20area%2C%20with%20some%20heading%20to%20Latakia%20(in%20Syria)%20and%20others%20to%20the%20Hermel%20area%20in%20Lebanon%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20source%20also%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20source%20close%20to%20Hezbollah%20earlier%20said%20it%20had%20sent%202%2C000%20fighters%20into%20Syria%2C%20to%20an%20area%20near%20the%20Lebanese%20border%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20defend%20its%20positions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Suddenly%20everyone%20was%20scared'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%20ministry%20earlier%20insisted%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20truth%20to%20news%20claiming%20our%20armed%20forces...%20have%20withdrawn%26quot%3B%20from%20positions%20near%20Damascus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Syrian%20army%20said%20that%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20area%20around%20Damascus%2C%20it%20was%20reinforcing%20positions%20in%20the%20south%2C%20and%20operations%20against%20the%20rebels%20were%20beginning%20in%20the%20Hama%2C%20Homs%20and%20Daraa%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFP%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20independently%20verify%20some%20of%20the%20information%20provided%20by%20the%20government%20and%20the%20rebels%2C%20as%20its%20journalists%20cannot%20reach%20the%20areas%20around%20Damascus%20where%20the%20rebels%20say%20they%20are%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20of%20the%20capital%20described%20to%20AFP%20a%20state%20of%20panic%20as%20traffic%20jams%20clogged%20the%20city%20centre%2C%20people%20sought%20supplies%20and%20queued%20to%20withdraw%20money%20from%20ATMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20was%20not%20like%20this%20when%20I%20left%20my%20house%20this%20morning...%20suddenly%20everyone%20was%20scared%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20woman%2C%20Rania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20kilometres%20(miles)%20away%2C%20the%20mood%20was%20starkly%20different.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Damascus%20suburb%2C%20witnesses%20said%20protesters%20toppled%20a%20statue%20of%20Assad's%20father%2C%20the%20late%20leader%20Hafez%20al-Assad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFPTV%20images%20from%20Hama%2C%20Syria's%20fourth-largest%20city%2C%20showed%20abandoned%20tanks%20and%20other%20armoured%20vehicles%2C%20one%20of%20them%20on%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHama%20resident%20Kharfan%20Mansour%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bhappy%20with%20the%20liberation%20of%20Hama%20and%20the%20liberation%20of%20Syria%20from%20the%20Assad%20regime%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoldiers%20'fled'%20to%20Iraq%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Observatory%20said%20government%20forces%20had%20ceded%20more%20key%20ground%2C%20losing%20control%20of%20all%20southern%20Daraa%20province%2C%20the%20cradle%20of%20the%202011%20uprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bredeploying%20and%20repositioning%26quot%3B%20in%20Daraa%20and%20another%20southern%20province%2C%20Sweida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Observatory%20also%20said%20troops%20were%20also%20evacuating%20posts%20in%20Quneitra%2C%20near%20the%20Israeli-annexed%20Golan%20Heights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJordan%20has%20urged%20its%20citizens%20to%20leave%20neighbouring%20Syria%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20possible%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20have%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Assad%20ally%20Russia%2C%20which%20both%20keep%20troops%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AFP%20correspondent%20in%20Daraa%20saw%20local%20fighters%20guarding%20public%20property%20and%20civil%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sweida%2C%20a%20local%20fighter%20told%20AFP%20that%20after%20government%20forces%20withdrew%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20their%20positions%20and%20headquarters%2C%20we%20are%20now%20securing%20and%20protecting%20vital%20facilities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Iraqi%20security%20source%20told%20AFP%20that%20Baghdad%20has%20allowed%20in%20hundreds%20of%20Syrian%20soldiers%2C%20who%20%26quot%3Bfled%20the%20front%20lines%26quot%3B%2C%20through%20the%20Al-Qaim%20border%20crossing.%20A%20second%20source%20put%20the%20figure%20at%202%2C000%20troops%2C%20including%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'War%2C%20blood%20and%20tears'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHTS%20is%20rooted%20in%20the%20Syrian%20branch%20of%20Al-Qaeda.%20Proscribed%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20Western%20governments%2C%20it%20has%20sought%20to%20soften%20its%20image%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20and%20told%20minority%20groups%20living%20in%20areas%20they%20now%20control%20not%20to%20worry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20offensive%20began%2C%20at%20least%20826%20people%2C%20mostly%20combatants%20but%20also%20including%20111%20civilians%2C%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20the%20Observatory%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20said%20the%20violence%20has%20displaced%20370%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20special%20envoy%20to%20Syria%2C%20Geir%20Pedersen%2C%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Burgent%20political%20talks%26quot%3B%20