questions%20still%20remain%20about%20the%20completeness%20of%20Syria's%20declaration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAttacks%20On%20Ghouta%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhouta%20bears%20witness%20to%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20chemical%20attacks%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Syria.%20The%20morning%20of%20August%2021%2C%202013%20captured%20a%20horror%20never%20seen%20before%20as%20the%20Assad%20regime%20carried%20out%20two%20chemical%20attacks%20on%20the%20opposition-controlled%20suburbs%20of%20Damascus.%20The%20attacks%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20hundreds%20of%20civilians%2C%20including%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fg5ecut2g_ghouta-chemical-attack-2013_625x300_08_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20surface-to-surface%20rocket%20system%20was%20used%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20attack%2C%20according%20to%20an%20investigation%20by%20Human%20Rights%20Watch.%20Sarin%2C%20an%20extremely%20potent%20nerve%20agent%2C%20was%20likely%20used%20in%20the%20attack%20as%20doctors%20said%20the%20victims%20showed%20symptoms%20of%20exposure%20to%20nerve%20gas%20-%20suffocation%2C%20nausea%2C%20frothing%20in%20the%20mouth%2C%20and%20fluids%20coming%20out%20of%20eyes%20and%20noses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenying%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20Syrian%20government%20had%20put%20the%20blame%20on%20the%20opposition%20groups.%20HRW%20claims%20that%20it%20has%20found%20no%20evidence%20that%20supported%20the%20Syrian%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20severity%20of%20the%20attack%20could%20be%20understood%20from%20the%20visuals%20-available%20online%20-%20showing%20rows%20of%20bodies%20of%20dead%20adults%20and%20children%20wrapped%20in%20white%20shrouds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Assad%20had%20carried%20out%20another%20chemical%20