a%20alliance%20won%20230%20of%20the%20288%20seats%20in%20the%20November%2020%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition's%20strength%20in%20the%20assembly%20is%20low%20but%20many%20young%20Opposition%20MLAs%20will%20show%20their%20mettle%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20sessions%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20state%20chief%20Abu%20Asim%20Azmi%20announcing%20that%20his%20party%20was%20pulling%20out%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20alliance%20after%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20hailed%2C%20in%20a%20newspaper%20advertisement%2C%20those%20who%20demolished%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20sought%20to%20play%20down%20the%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20Akhilesh%20Yadav-led%20party%20was%20of%20the%20firm%20view%20that%20the%20Opposition's%20unity%20is%20necessary%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20can%20not%20demand%20that%20a%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20must%20be%20appointed%20as%20they%20do%20not%20have%20the%20required%20numbers%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20Mr%20Pawar-led%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20Congress%20or%20Sena%20(UBT)%20individually%20have%20the%20minimum%2029%20MLAs%20--%20ten%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20Assembly's%20strength%20--%20to%20be%20eligible%20to%20get%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%2C%20however%2C%20noted%20that%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20when%20his%20own%20party%20was%20reduced%20to%20just%20six%20MLAs%20following%20defections%2C%20he%20still%20became%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20for%20a%20year%20followed%20by%20Mrinal%20Gore%20and%20Nihal%20Ahmed%20as%20the%20Opposition%20decided%20to%20rotate%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20about%20the%20row%20over%20a%20wad%20of%20Rs%20500%20notes%20being%20found%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%2C%20himself%20a%20mem