ing%20figure%20that%20mirrored%20the%20quick%20rise%20of%20her%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Trump%2C%20now%20the%20president-elect%2C%20defeated%20Harris%20in%20the%20general%20election%2C%20with%20the%20vice%20president%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharris-trump-blue-wall-democrats-suburban-voters-unions-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoming%20up%20short%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20swing%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocquery.fec.gov%2Fcgi-bin%2Fforms%2FC00703975%2F1858333%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20federal%20filings%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%20that%20the%20Harris%20campaign%20had%20%241.8%20million%20remaining%20in%20the%20bank%20after%20spending%20over%20%241%20billion%20against%20Trump%20in%20the%20presidential%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20filings%2C%20the%20Harris%20campaign%20also%20reported%20that%20it%20had%20no%20debts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filings%20reveal%20the%20pace%20of%20spending%20for%20the%20Harris%20campaign%2C%20which%20began%20with%20heightened%20enthusiasm%20from%20Democrats%20and%20major%20donors%20who%20had%20grown%20despondent%20over%20Biden's%20chances%20after%20a%20disastrous%20debate%20against%20Trump%20raised%20questions%20about%20his%20ability%20to%20mount%20a%20robust%20reelection%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20October%2017%20through%20November%2025%2C%20which%20included%20some%20of%20the%20most%20frenzied%20stretches%20of%20the%20campaign%20through%20the%20postelection%20period%2C%20Harris%20raised%20%24160%20million%20and%20spent%20over%20%24270%20million.%20The%20Trump%20campaign%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocquery.fec.gov%2Fcgi-bin%2Fforms%2FC00828541%2F1858277%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraked%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0nearly%20%2487%20million%20during%20that%20same%20period%C2%A0and%20spent%20%24113%20million%2C%20the%20president-elect's%20campaign%20filings%20indicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F