12%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edined%20at%20Hell's%20Kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gordon%20Ramsay's%20restaurant%20based%20on%20the%20show%20of%20the%20same%20name.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20longtime%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgilmore-girls-interesting-things-about-lorelai-fun-facts-2022-10%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efan%20of%20the%20TV%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20loved%20how%20closely%20the%20restaurant%20resembled%20the%20show's%20set.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20also%20thought%20the%20prices%20were%20surprisingly%20reasonable%20considering%20the%20high%20quality%20of%20the%20food.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20kid%2C%20I%20couldn't%20get%20enough%20of%20reality%20competition%20shows.%20I%20never%20missed%20an%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ficonic-american-idol-stars-where-are-they-now-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Idol%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BSo%20You%20Think%20You%20Can%20Dance%26quot%3B%20and%20loved%20the%20feel-good%20nature%20of%20the%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20I%20got%20my%20first%20glimpse%20of%20a%20very%20different%20type%20of%20reality%20show%20%E2%80%94%20one%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-chef-recipe-for-apple-pie-review-photos-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecelebrity%20chef%20Gordon%20Ramsay%3C%2Fa%3E%20shouted%20at%20contestants%20for%20overcooking%20scallops%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20hooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHell's%20Kitchen%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20first%20premiered%20in%20the%20US%20on%20Fox%20in%202005%20and%20is%20now%20in%20its%2023rd%20season%2C%20follows%20chefs%20competing%20in%20various%20challenges%20in%20hopes%20of%20becoming%20a%20head%20chef%20at%20a%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20since%20been%20nominated%20for%20five%20Emmys%2C%20and%20its%20star%2C%20Ramsay%2C%20even%20opened%20a%20chain%20of%20restaurants%20based%20on%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant%20has%20seven%20locations%20in%20places%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-restaurants-in-miami-from-local-foodie-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELas%20Vegas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Miami%2C%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20Lake%20Tahoe%2C%20though%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20had%20dinner%20at%20the%20one%20in%20Atlantic%20City%2C%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20things%20that%20surprised%20me%20most%20about%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20couldn't%20believe%20how%20much%20the%20restaurant%20resembled%20the%20show's%20set.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223325%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20busy%20restaurant%20with%20an%20open%20kitchen.%20The%20left%20half%20of%20the%20kitchen%20has%20red%20decor%20and%20the%20right%20half%20has%20blue%20decor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674f3910e45a68623a279254%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222494%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20was%20visible%20from%20the%20dining%20area%20and%20had%20chefs%20broken%20up%20into%20red%20and%20blue%20%26quot%3Bteams.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EStephanie%20Pitera%20Statile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20walked%20into%20the%20restaurant%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20by%20how%20familiar%20the%20main%20dining%20area%20looked.%20I%20felt%20as%20though%20I%20had%20stumbled%20onto%20the%20set%20of%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20restaurant's%20website%2C%20emulating%20the%20show%20was%20intentional.%20The%20kitchen%2C%20which%20was%20visible%20from%20the%20dining%20area%2C%20even%20had%20chefs%20broken%20up%20into%20red%20and%20blue%20%26quot%3Bteams%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20just%20like%20on%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20subtle%20theming%20was%20everywhere.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223578%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20hold%20half-full%20Champagne%20glasses%20garnished%20with%20strawberries%20on%20pitchfork-themed%20toothpicks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674f394f9e9761932b4a59a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222684%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20show's%20signature%20pitchforks%20were%20even%20on%20our%20drinks.%3Cp%3EStephanie%20Pitera%20Statile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20ate%20at%20Hell's%20Kitchen%20as%20part%20of%20our%20anniversary%20celebration%2C%20so%20we%20were%20surprised%20with%20complimentary%20glasses%20of%20sparkling%20wine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20glasses%20were%20topped%20with%20strawberries%20pierced%20with%20toothpicks%20shaped%20like%20pitchforks%2C%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20show's%20logo.%20The%20theming%20didn't%20stop%20there%20%E2%80%94%20the%20lighting%20fixtures%20hanging%20from%20the%20ceiling%20were%20also%20shaped%20like%20pitchforks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20details%20were%20the%20bathroom%20doors%20marked%20with%20pitchforks%20resembling%20a%20%26quot%3BW%26quot%3B%20for%20women%20and%20an%20%26quot%3BM%26quot%3B%20for%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDuring%20my%20visit%2C%20the%20chefs%20in%20the%20kitchen%20seemed%20much%20happier%20than%20they%20do%20on%20TV.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223847%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20giant%2C%20golden%20Hell's%20Kitchen%20restaurant%20logo%20that%20features%20the%20letters%20%26quot%3BH%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BK%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20pitchfork%20in%20the%20middle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673268e25ec9bfa3d63d5435%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222885%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnlike%20on%20the%20show%2C%20we%20didn't%20hear%20any%20yelling%20inside%20the%20restaurant.%3Cp%3EStephanie%20Pitera%20Statile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20secret%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20screaming%20happens%20on%20the%20set%20of%20%26quot%3BHell's%20Kitchen.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20restaurant%20of%20the%20same%20name%2C%20however%2C%20I%20was%20pleased%20to%20see%20the%20chefs%20laughing%20and%20chatting%20with%20each%20other%20as%20they%20prepared%20our%20meals.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20fun%20as%20it%20is%20to%20see%20Ramsay%20shout%20on%20TV%2C%20I%20was%20happy%20not%20to%20hear%20yelling%20during%20our%20dinner.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20menu%20actually%20featured%20many%20of%20the%20show's%20signature%20dishes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yellow%20risotto%20on%20a%20white%20plate%2C%20topped%20with%20fennel%2C%20a%20lobster%20tail%2C%20and%20basil.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67326e8c5ec9bfa3d63d5af8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20thoroughly%20enjoyed%20the%20lobster%20risotto.%3Cp%3EStephanie%20Pitera%20Statile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20think%20of%20%26quot%3BHell's%20Kitchen%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20immediately%20think%20of%20dishes%20like%20beef%20Wellington%2C%20scallops%2C%20and%20risotto.%20They're%20cooked%20often%20on%20the%20show%20and%20are%20some%20of%20Ramsay's%20signatures.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20to%20find%20all%20these%20items%20and%20more%20on%20the%20restaurant's%20menu.%20And%2C%20yes%2C%20the%20risotto%20certainly%20lived%20up%20to%20the%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EConsidering%20the%20high%20quality%20of%20the%20meal%2C%20I%20thought%20the%20prices%20were%20surprisingly%20fair.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20plate%20with%20three%20scallops%20sitting%20in%20a%20swirl%20of%20puree%20and%20topped%20with%20lardons%2C%20fennel%2C%20and%20chives%2C%20and%20a%20cast-iron%20skillet%20of%20meatballs%20topped%20with%20cheese%2C%20croutons%2C%20basil%2C%20and%20red%20sauce.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67326dc65ec9bfa3d63d5a7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20thought%20our%20meal%20at%20Hell's%20Kitchen%20was%20a%20great%20value.%3Cp%3EStephanie%20Pitera%20Statile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20made%20a%20reservation%20at%20Hell's%20Kitchen%2C%20I%20expected%20our%20meal%20would%20be%20quite%20expensive.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20can%20easily%20spend%20%2450%20on%20dinner%20at%20our%20local%20diner%2C%20and%20this%20is%20a%20TV-famous%20restaurant%20serving%20some%20high-class%20dishes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20we%20got%20three%20appetizers%2C%20an%20entr%C3%A9e%2C%20and%20a%20dessert%20cocktail%20for%20%24216%2C%20including%20tax%20and%20tip.%20Considering%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20meal%20and%20the%20immersive%20atmosphere%2C%20I%20thought%20this%20price%20was%20surprisingly%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgordon-ramsay-hells-kitchen-restaurant-what-its-really-like-surprising-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733581622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674f42009e9761932b4a5d1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgordon-ramsay-hells-kitchen-restaurant-what-its-really-like-surprising-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20ate%20at%20Gordon%20Ramsay's%20Hell's%20Kitchen%20restaurant%20based%20on%20the%20Fox%20show.%20From%20prices%20to%20decor%2C%20here's%20what%20surprised%20me%20about%20the%20experience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Stephanie%20Pitera%20Statile)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgordon-ramsay-hells-kitchen-restaurant-what-its-really-like-surprising-2024-12%22%2