20for%20local%20food%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20end%20up%20making%20daal%20bati%2C%20thinking%20that%E2%80%99s%20all%20we%20have%20the%20taste%20for.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20Dipali%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Western%20influences%20increasingly%20permeate%20local%20cultures%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F322885%2Fkarnataka-shivaranjini-started-suggi-oota-south-indian-restaurant-in-california%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20habits%20are%20facing%20a%20decline.%20A%20sense%20of%20cultural%20inferiority%20often%20leads%20rural%20and%20tribal%20people%20to%20shy%20away%20from%20their%20traditional%20cuisine%2C%20making%20them%20reluctant%20to%20share%20or%20record%20their%20recipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20an%20experience%20working%20with%20a%20weaving%20cluster%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20have%20our%20meals%20at%20different%20homes%20each%20day.%20However%2C%20one%20particularly%20hot%20summer%20day%2C%20I%20developed%20a%20headache%20and%20lost%20my%20appetite.%20I%20declined%20the%20%3Cem%3Ealoo%20chole%20puri%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20was%20prepared%20for%20me%20and%20instead%20requested%20the%20same%20%3Cem%3Echaas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eroti%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20her%20son%20was%20eating.%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EChaas%20roti%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20simply%20buttermilk%20and%20chapati%20is%20often%20made%20during%20the%20summers%20when%20it%20gets%20too%20hot%20to%20cook%20on%20an%20open%20fire%20mud%20stove.%20The%20dish%20is%20simple%2C%20made%20with%20leftover%20dried%20chapati%20bites%20crushed%20into%20a%20bowl%20of%20cold%20buttermilk%20with%20onions%2C%20mint%2C%20green%20chillies%20and%20salt.%20It%20is%20a%20naturally%20cooling%20recipe%20that%20protects%20from%20the%20strong%20gusts%20of%20loo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20she%20said%20it%20in%20front%20of%20her%20son%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20something%20I%20would%20like%20because%20it%20is%20the%20food%20of%20%3Cem%3Edehati%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20derogatory%20term%20for%20villagers).%20I%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20one%20incident%2C%20I%20can%20never%20take%20out%20of%20my%20head%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dipali%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20any%20urban-looking%20person%20asks%20them%20for%20local%20food%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20end%20up%20making%20%3Cem%3Edaal%20bati%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Lentil%20and%20wheat%20bread%20balls)%2C%20thinking%20that%E2%80%99s%20all%20we%20have%20the%20taste%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reflects.%20The%20pressure%20to%20conform%20to%20urban%20food%20preferences%20and%20the%20commercialisation%20of%20local%20food%20culture%20was%20evident.%20But%20the%20irony%2C%20as%20Dipali%20found%2C%20was%20that%20these%20people%20were%20sitting%20on%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20unique%2C%20locally%20grown%2C%20and%20indigenous%20foods%20%E2%80%94%20foods%20that%20were%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20being%20lost%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Dipali%E2%80%99s%20journey%20began%20as%20a%20personal%20quest%20to%20understand%20her%20roots.%20This%20led%20her%20to%20embark%20on%20in-depth%20research%2C%20exploring%20the%20remote%20corners%20of%20Rajasthan.%20She%20meticulously%20documented%20local%20eating%20habits%2C%20indigenous%20ingredients%2C%20their%20seasonal%20availability%2C%20storage%20techniques%2C%20and%20the%20diverse%20recipes%20they%20inspired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20broadly%20identifies%20nine%20cultural%20zones%20in%20Rajasthan%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20geography%2C%20the%20agricultural%20features%2C%20and%20language.%20Due%20to%20its%20location%2C%20Marwar%2C%20or%20the%20desert%20region%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20has%20always%20depended%20on%20forged%20ingredients%20instead%20of%20greens.%20Ingredients%20like%3Cem%3E%20pholga%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Efogla%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Cooling%20food)%3Cem%3E%2C%20ber%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Rajasthani%20Plum)%3Cem%3E%2C%20ker%20shangri%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Caper%20berry)%20are%20commonly%20consumed.%20Most%20of%20the%20Rajasthani%20food%20served%20around%20the%20country%20like%20%3Cem%3Elaal%20maas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Red%20Meat%20Curry)%3Cem%3E%2C%20daal%20bati%2C%20ker%20shangri%20ki%20sabzi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Caper%20berry%20curry)%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eall%20come%20from%20these%20regions.%20But%20what%20about%20the%20rest%20of%20it%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202700px)%20100vw%2C%202700px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FRajasthan-Cultural-Zones-Map-_page-0001-1_11zon-1733392276.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20map%20showcasing%20the%20nine%20cultural%20zones%20of%20Rajasthan%20according%20to%20their%20districts%2C%20made%20by%20The%20Kindness%20Meal.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FRajasthan-Cultural-Zones-Map-_page-0001-1_11zon-1733392276.jpg%202700w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FRajasthan-Cultural-Zones-Map-_page-0001-1_11zon-1733392276-300x233.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FRajasthan-Cultural-Zones-Map-_page-0001-1_11zon-1733392276-500x389.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FRajasthan-Cultural-Zones-Map-_page-0001-1_11zon-1733392276-768x597.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FRajasthan-Cultural-Zones-Map-_page-0001-1_11zon-1733392276-1536x1195.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FRajasthan-Cultural-Zones-Map-_page-