ajasthan.%20There%20are%20ingredients%20and%20foods%20that%20people%20are%20free%20to%20taste%20along%20with%20other%20components%20such%20as%20photo%20essays%2C%20audio%20stories%2C%20artworks.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20Rajasthani%20people%20come%20and%20tell%20us%20that%20they%20have%20heard%20about%20these%20ingredients%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20first%20time%20seeing%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20creation%20is%20made%20of%20multiple%20components%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20that%20if%20I%E2%80%99m%20taking%20it%20to%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20it%20should%20make%20the%20viewer%20think%20not%20just%20about%20my%20culture%20but%20also%20of%20their%20own.%20I%20want%20this%20to%20be%20a%20touch%20point%20where%20somebody%20interacts%20with%20it%2C%20they%20go%20back%20home%20and%20call%20their%20mother%2C%20asking%20about%20an%20ingredient%20or%20for%20a%20recipe.%20Something%20they%20used%20to%20have%20as%20a%20child%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Dipali%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFood%20is%20not%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20entertainment%20or%20sustenance.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20an%20identity.%E2%80%9D%20And%20through%20her%20work%2C%20she%20is%20ensuring%20that%20the%20rich%20culinary%20traditions%20of%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%94%20and%20beyond%20%E2%80%94%20are%20preserved%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%2C%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Dipali%20Khandelwal%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733466538000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FDipali-with-Maa_11zon-1733391791.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D386500%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20a%20deep%20commitment%20to%20preserving%20Rajasthan's%20food%20traditions%2C%20Dipali%20Khandelwal%20is%20documenting%20and%20sharin