acy-education-government-schools-volunteer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacademic%20journey%20for%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20providing%20a%20digital%20identifier%20that%20links%20their%20educational%20records%20across%20multiple%20institutions%2C%20both%20within%20India%20and%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20type%20of%20academic%20information%20can%20be%20stored%20in%20the%20APAAR%20ID%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APAAR%20ID%20is%20a%20unique%2012-digit%20code%20allowing%20students%20to%20digitally%20store%2C%20manage%2C%20and%20access%20a%20comprehensive%20range%20of%20academic%20information.%20This%20includes%20scorecards%2C%20marksheets%2C%20grade%20sheets%2C%20degrees%2C%20diplomas%2C%20certificates%2C%20and%20co-curricular%20achievements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20ensures%20smoother%20transitions%20between%20different%20educational%20stages%20and%20institutions%2C%20offering%20significant%20benefits%20for%20students%20pursuing%20education%20across%20various%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECan%20you%20access%20academic%20records%20anytime%2C%20or%20is%20there%20a%20specific%20process%20to%20follow%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAPAAR%20integrates%20with%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC)%2C%20enabling%20students%20to%20accumulate%2C%20transfer%2C%20and%20redeem%20credits%20across%20institutions.%20This%20system%20not%20only%20facilitates%20credit%20transfers%20but%20also%20tracks%20academic%20achievements%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20students%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363045%2Fgrassroots-organisations-initiatives-changemakers-teach-education-underprivileged-children-slum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanage%20their%20educational%20progress%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20students%20can%20access%20their%20academic%20records%20anytime%2C%20as%20it%20consolidates%20all%20their%20achievements%20onto%20a%20single%20platform%2C%20creating%20a%20comprehensive%20digital%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20the%20requirements%20for%20applying%20for%20an%20APAAR%20ID%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20generating%20an%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20important%20prerequisites%20to%20consider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20the%20UDISE%2B%20(Unified%20District%20Information%20System%20for%20Education%20Plus)%20records%20must%20match%20exactly%20with%20the%20name%20as%20per%20their%20Aadhaar.%20This%20ensures%20consistency%20and%20accuracy%20in%20the%20identification%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20Personal%20Education%20Number%20(PEN)%20is%20mandatory%20for%20generating%20the%20APAAR%20ID.%20It%20is%20a%20unique%20identification%20number%20for%20students%20across%20all%20the%20education%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIs%20APAAR%20ID%20only%20useful%20for%20current%20students%2C%20or%20can%20it%20benefit%20graduates%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APAAR%20ID%20is%20beneficial%20not%20only%20for%20current%20students%20but%20also%20for%20graduates.%20For%20students%20like%20Krystelle%20Dsouza%2C%20a%20journalist%20pursuing%20her%20master%E2%80%99s