rget%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20a%20DigiLocker%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20logging%20in%20with%20your%20credentials%2C%20DigiLocker%20will%20prompt%20you%20to%20consent%20to%20share%20your%20Aadhaar%20card%20details%20with%20ABC%20for%20KYC%20verification.%20Once%20you%20agree%2C%20enter%20your%20academic%20details%2C%20such%20as%20your%20school%20or%20university%20name%2C%20class%2C%20and%20course.%20After%20submitting%20the%20form%2C%20your%20APAAR%20ID%20card%20will%20be%20generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20you%20download%20your%20APAAR%20ID%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APAAR%20ID%20can%20be%20easily%20downloaded%20by%20logging%20into%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC%20Bank)%20website.%20Once%20logged%20in%2C%20students%20can%20navigate%20to%20the%20dashboard%20and%20select%20the%20%E2%80%98APAAR%20card%20download%E2%80%99%20option.%20The%20card%20will%20then%20appear%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20ready%20to%20be%20downloaded%20or%20printed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDisclaimer%3A%20We%20will%20update%20the%20latest%20information%20about%20the%20APAAR%20ID%20card%20when%20more%20details%20are%20revealed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733318268000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-mobile-1732080263.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D386210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20launched%20in%202023%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20provides%20a%20digital%20identity%20that%20helps%20st